        { speaker: 'B', chinese: '很多不同。比如中国人吃饭的时候喜欢大家一起分享菜。', pinyin: 'hen3 duo1 bu4 tong2. bi3 ru2 zhong1 guo2 ren2 chi1 fan4 de shi2 hou4 xi3 huan1 da4 jia1 yi4 qi3 fen1 xiang3 cai4.', meaning: 'Many differences. For example, Chinese people like to share dishes together when eating.' },
        { speaker: 'A', chinese: '对，这叫合餐制。还有呢？', pinyin: 'dui4, zhe4 jiao4 he2 can1 zhi4. hai2 you3 ne?', meaning: 'Yes, this is called shared dining. What else?' },
        { speaker: 'B', chinese: '中国人很重视家庭。过年的时候全家都要团聚。', pinyin: 'zhong1 guo2 ren2 hen3 zhong4 shi4 jia1 ting2. guo4 nian2 de shi2 hou4 quan2 jia1 dou1 yao4 tuan2 ju4.', meaning: 'Chinese people value family a lot. During Chinese New Year, the whole family gets together.' },
        { speaker: 'A', chinese: '这是很重要的传统。你喜欢这里的生活方式吗？', pinyin: 'zhe4 shi4 hen3 zhong4 yao4 de chuan2 tong3. ni3 xi3 huan1 zhe4 li3 de sheng1 huo2 fang1 shi4 ma?', meaning: 'This is a very important tradition. Do you like the lifestyle here?' },
        { speaker: 'B', chinese: '我很喜欢。虽然一开始有些不习惯，但现在觉得很温馨。', pinyin: 'wo3 hen3 xi3 huan1. sui1 ran2 yi4 kai1 shi3 you3 xie1 bu4 xi2 guan4, dan4 xian4 zai4 jue2 de hen3 wen1 xin1.', meaning: 'I like it a lot. Although it was a bit hard to get used to at first, now I find it very warm and welcoming.' },
        { speaker: 'A', chinese: '听到你这么说我很高兴！', pinyin: 'ting1 dao4 ni3 zhe4 me shuo1 wo3 hen3 gao1 xing4!', meaning: 'I am glad to hear you say that!' }
